text: The Henschel Hs 123 is a biplane built in Nazi Germany as a dive bomber. Known like a Sturzkampfflugzeug this single-engine was used for the Spanish Civil War and after for the World War II against Polish, Belgian, and French troops. Spanish air force used some Hs 123. == Bibliography == * Category:World War II German aircraft Category:Military of Germany Category:German military aircraft
title: Henschel Hs 123
